It's due to indentation problem of user_op.py, and after fixing identation, I forget to pip uninstall first.
After pip uninstall and re generate wll and reinstall now I can find tensorflow.user_ops.zero_out.
So now no problem, but still no ./bazel-genfiles/tensorflow/cc/ops/user_ops.{h,cc}(no dir cc under ./bazel-genfiles/tensorflow/) as the wiki said, may be not a problem, if so please close this issue @josh11b
